 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EAscertia provides products and services which relate to digital signature creation, verification, eID validation, time stamping and  other PKI infrastructure.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThese products allow small, medium or large enterprises to secure their valuable data be it PDF, XML, raw files, Office documents etc.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe digital signature format supported by Ascertia\u0026#8217;s products for both signing and verification are CMS, CAdES, XAdEs, PKCS#7, PDF Signatures, PAdES, S/Mime, PKCS#1\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe products are offered in the form of  desktop, server or web based solutions. Ascertia\u0026#8217;s flag ship product TrustFinder OCSP Server is also JITC certified: http://jitc.fhu.disa.mil/pki/pke\u003Cem\u003Elab/ocsp\u003C/em\u003Etesting/ocsp_testing.html\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EPKI infrastructure products cover aspects like OCSP, Timestamping, XKMS, SCVP and Certification Authority\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAscertia also provides free or cheap digital certificates which are  aimed for trial or test environments.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EAscertia has recently launched a cloud based document signing/collaboration service for e-signature and digital signatures called SigningHub (http://www.signinghub.com)\u003C/p\u003E",
